00:05:06.839 --> 00:05:09.108
Do that, because they have
interesting recordings

00:05:09.108 --> 00:05:10.843
of different--

00:05:10.843 --> 00:05:13.146
like, people from Guadulupe,
people from Martinique,

00:05:13.146 --> 00:05:15.515
Gauguin, Mauritius
speaking the creole.

00:05:15.515 --> 00:05:18.151
They even have
